snippet.title: F1 Race Stars Trailer
snippet.description:
F1 Race Stars Trailer. F1 Race Stars will deliver 4-player split-screen racing and 12-player competition alongside an extensive career mode in a world tour of iconic Formula One locations ! Join us on Facebook : http://facebook.com/GameNewsOfficial !

F1 Race Stars Trailer. The game is coming this november for the PS3, Xbox 360 and PC. Subscribe now get the upcoming gameplay trailers !
